  "title": "Storekeeper / Warehouse Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>We’re looking for someone with warehouse operations experience to support our growth. This is also an exciting opportunity to learn and grow as we are transforming our warehouse operations as part of an overall digital transformation initiative.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Scope of responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>- Receive and process incoming packages and materials, including fabricated and electronic parts</p>\n<p>- Prepare and pack outgoing packages and materials, including fabricated and electronic parts and equipment</p>\n<p>- Perform housekeeping tasks in warehouse and keep warehouse neat and tidy</p>\n<p>- Perform continuous improvement projects to improve warehouse operations</p>\n<p>- Responsible for the upkeeping of stock inventory in warehouse</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<p>- Minimum 3 years’ work experience in warehouse operations (electronics or manufacturing environment)</p>\n<p>- Proficient in the use of Microsoft Office applications, including Excel</p>\n<p>- (Good to have) Familiar with use of ERP system to manage warehouse operations</p>\n<p>- Proactive, detail-oriented, and able to thrive in a fast-paced project environment</p>",
